{"tid":1933483,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎個friend】劇名含侮辱性 《李屍朝鮮》播出兩季後改名","createTime":"2020-03-19T10:12:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T00:01:47.000Z","uid":117837,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"cd5186a3e87f7084bfce049a459af4b006778efb","tid":1933483,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/3/1584602270_tT-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F3%2F1584602270_tT-1280w.jpg&h=599d144d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNetflix熱播南韓原創劇集《李屍朝鮮》，本月播出第二季後，引來劇迷熱烈討論，但有南韓網民提出，《李屍朝鮮》的中譯名稱，帶有侮辱性而要求Netflix更改處名。<br />\n<br />\n原來「李氏朝鮮」於韓國人的歷史裡，是日本殖民統治下的蔑稱，而且加入一個「屍」諧音，更讓不少南韓網民感到有問題，因為此劇的韓語及英語片名，是用「王國」或「Kingdom」，Netflix對此亦作出回應：「Netflix 感謝各方對於原創韓劇《李屍朝鮮》中文片名的相關意見與賜教，我們已充分了解並將會盡快做出修改，並盡速再發布通知公告。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/3/1584602272_KQ-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F3%2F1584602272_KQ-1280w.jpg&h=912d88ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/%E5%8A%87%E5%90%8D%E5%90%AB%E4%BE%AE%E8%BE%B1%E6%80%A7-%E3%80%8A%E6%9D%8E%E5%B1%8D%E6%9C%9D%E9%AE%AE%E3%80%8B%E6%92%AD%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A9%E5%AD%A3%E5%BE%8C%E6%94%B9%E5%90%8D-212016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F%25E5%258A%2587%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2590%25AB%25E4%25BE%25AE%25E8%25BE%25B1%25E6%2580%25A7-%25E3%2580%258A%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25B1%258D%25E6%259C%259D%25E9%25AE%25AE%25E3%2580%258B%25E6%2592%25AD%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25AD%25A3%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2590%258D-212016&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFT11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=1ab93332\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/%E5%8A%87%E5%90%8D%E5%90%AB%E4%BE%AE%E8%BE%B1%E6%80%A7-%E3%80%8A%E6%9D%8E%E5%B1%8D%E6%9C%9D%E9%AE%AE%E3%80%8B%E6%92%AD%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A9%E5%AD%A3%E5%BE%8C%E6%94%B9%E5%90%8D-212016</a>"},{"pid":"8285462174424e6391ff900747c6d134e75f83ba","tid":1933483,"uid":117837,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:21:41.000Z","msg":"以前有套港產cult片叫生化壽屍<br />\n唔知有冇侮日 使唔使改名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0556ecbf7e2859f9b038d90ce1888cf87365d8","tid":1933483,"uid":41343,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:33:53.000Z","msg":"《新型病毒-15XX（來源地不能夠肯定）》"},{"pid":"1bae756ff892e7498c728d124c1e54301558fa2c","tid":1933483,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:34:34.000Z","msg":"神的國度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3655e3ecaace99a1dc0a98966c9ebd13f2246d","tid":1933483,"uid":12269,"like":101,"dislike":0,"score":101,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:35:26.000Z","msg":"叫《陳國邦朝鮮》囉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VB5YJY3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVB5YJY3.jpg&h=84f4867c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"282031055b08c562fa1d74dace95e77d5c0921af","tid":1933483,"uid":228995,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"de3655e3ecaace99a1dc0a98966c9ebd13f2246d","tid":1933483,"uid":12269,"like":101,"dislike":0,"score":101,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:35:26.000Z","msg":"叫《陳國邦朝鮮》囉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VB5YJY3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVB5YJY3.jpg&h=84f4867c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:35:47.000Z","msg":"silly朝鮮"},{"pid":"960cb8344b0fefab9dea68f4bc5ee704c8ad69e2","tid":1933483,"uid":313514,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:37:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4725ca838db320befbeb860c31f8f50eaec4b57d","tid":1933483,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco